  <!-- PROCESSO -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">Il metodo</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Dalla tua idea all'app live in <span style="color: var(--brand-primary);">7 step collaudati</span></h2>
        <p class="section-lead">Un processo ripetuto su 50+ progetti. Trasparente, prevedibile, focalizzato sulla tua crescita.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-timeline">
        <div class="process-step">
          <span class="step-num">1</span>
          <h3>Discovery &amp; Analisi</h3>
          <span class="step-duration">⏱ 3-5 giorni</span>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Comprendere a fondo la tua idea, obiettivi business, target utenti.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Kickoff meeting:</strong> idea, pain points, soluzione</li>
            <li><strong>Analisi competitor:</strong> app simili su store, identificazione gap</li>
            <li><strong>Definizione MVP:</strong> feature essenziali vs nice-to-have</li>
            <li><strong>Scelta tecnologica:</strong> native vs cross-platform, backend necessario</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="deliverable">📦 <strong>Deliverable:</strong> documento analisi con roadmap, tech stack, budget preliminare</div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <span class="step-num">2</span>
          <h3>UX / UI Design</h3>
          <span class="step-duration">⏱ 1-2 settimane</span>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Design intuitivo, brand-consistent, accessibile WCAG.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Wireframes</strong> e flussi di navigazione</li>
            <li><strong>Mockup high-fidelity</strong> con colori, font, icone</li>
            <li><strong>Prototipo interattivo</strong> Figma navigabile</li>
            <li><strong>Design system</strong> con componenti riutilizzabili</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="deliverable">📦 <strong>Deliverable:</strong> mockup finali, prototipo Figma, design system documentato</div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <span class="step-num">3</span>
          <h3>Setup Backend &amp; API</h3>
          <span class="step-duration">⏱ 1 settimana</span>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Infrastruttura cloud scalabile, sicura, performante.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Stack:</strong> Node.js/NestJS o Firebase, PostgreSQL/MongoDB</li>
            <li><strong>API</strong> REST o GraphQL, JWT, rate limiting</li>
            <li><strong>Database design:</strong> schema, indici, ottimizzazioni</li>
            <li><strong>Push notifications</strong> (FCM) setup</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="deliverable">📦 <strong>Deliverable:</strong> backend funzionante, API documentate (Swagger), environment staging</div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <span class="step-num">4</span>
          <h3>Sviluppo App Mobile</h3>
          <span class="step-duration">⏱ 4-10 settimane</span>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Clean code, architettura solida, test automatizzati.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>iOS:</strong> Swift + SwiftUI/UIKit, MVVM, Combine/async-await</li>
            <li><strong>Android:</strong> Kotlin + Jetpack Compose, MVVM, Coroutines</li>
            <li><strong>Cross-platform:</strong> Flutter (Dart) o React Native (TypeScript)</li>
            <li><strong>CI/CD:</strong> GitHub Actions, build automatiche, staging</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="deliverable">📦 <strong>Deliverable:</strong> app funzionante su staging, test coverage &gt;70%</div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <span class="step-num">5</span>
          <h3>Testing &amp; QA</h3>
          <span class="step-duration">⏱ 1-2 settimane</span>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Zero bug critici, stabilità su tutti i device.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Test multi-device:</strong> iPhone, iPad, Android (Samsung, Pixel)</li>
            <li><strong>Test performance:</strong> memoria, batteria, network 3G/4G/5G</li>
            <li><strong>Test sicurezza:</strong> penetration test, OWASP Mobile Top 10</li>
            <li><strong>UAT</strong> con utenti reali</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="deliverable">📦 <strong>Deliverable:</strong> bug report, app stabile pronta per gli store</div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <span class="step-num">6</span>
          <h3>Pubblicazione Store</h3>
          <span class="step-duration">⏱ 3-7 giorni</span>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">App live su App Store e Google Play, compliance totale.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Store listing:</strong> titolo, descrizione, screenshot, video preview, ASO keywords</li>
            <li><strong>Privacy &amp; Terms</strong> GDPR-compliant</li>
            <li><strong>Apple/Google review</strong> + gestione rejection</li>
            <li><strong>Rollout progressivo:</strong> 10% → 50% → 100%</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="deliverable">📦 <strong>Deliverable:</strong> app pubblicata, analytics configurati, monitoring attivo</div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <span class="step-num">7</span>
          <h3>Supporto Post-Lancio</h3>
          <span class="step-duration">⏱ ongoing</span>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Manutenzione, bug fix, nuove feature, aggiornamenti OS.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Monitoring 24/7:</strong> Crashlytics, performance, error tracking</li>
            <li><strong>Bug fix prioritari</strong> entro 24-48h</li>
            <li><strong>Aggiornamenti OS:</strong> compatibilità iOS/Android nuove versioni</li>
            <li><strong>Report mensili:</strong> utenti, retention, funnel conversione</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="deliverable">📦 <strong>Deliverable:</strong> SLA maintenance, update regolari, report analytics</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONFRONTO TECNOLOGIE -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">Scelta Tecnologica</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Native o Cross-Platform? <span style="color: var(--brand-primary);">Ti guido io.</span></h2>
        <p class="section-lead">Nessun approccio è "migliore" in assoluto: dipende da budget, obiettivi, tipo di app. Ecco un confronto onesto.</p>
